 \because\overline{AB}\parallel\overline{CD}\\ \therefore\angle{ACD}=\angle{CAB}=45^\circ\\ \therefore\widehat{AD}=\widehat{BC}=90^\circ\\ \because\widehat{AB}+\widehat{CD}+\widehat{AD}+\widehat{BC}=360^\circ\\ \therefore\widehat{AB}+\widehat{CD}=360^\circ-(\widehat{AD}+\widehat{BC})=180^\circ\\ \because\widehat{AB}=2\widehat{CD}\\ \therefore\widehat{CD}=180^\circ\div3=60^\circ\\ \therefore\widehat{CD}=\frac{60^\circ}{360^\circ}\times2\pi\times8=\frac{8\pi}{3} 
